    <title>History of Video Games</title>
   </head>
   <body>
     <h1>The beginnings</h1>
     <p>In October 1958, Physicist William Higinbotham created what is thought to be the first video game. It was a very simple tennis game, similar to the classic 1970s video game Pong, and it was quite a hit at a Brookhaven National Laboratory open house.</p>
   </body>
</html>
